Loops: everytime we have of group of something and we want to perform some repetitive tasks
1. while loop
2. for loop
3. advanced for loop [for each loop]


=> while loop
define a variable or use an already existing variable;
while(defineTheConditionOverVariable)
{
   code here will execute only if condition is true;
   I/D operator;
}

=> for loop
for(define a variable or use an already existing variable; defineTheConditionOverVariable;I/D operator)
{
   code here will execute only if condition is true;
}

=> advanced for loop [for each loop]

for(dataTypeOfGroup m: NameOfGroupOrCollection)
{
  perform action over m;
}

while/for || advanced for loop